      • parseUserID

        public int parseUserID​(JSONObject response,
                       IJsonParseError parseErrorListener)
        Returns a user ID from the JSON response of a given network request.
        Parameters:
        response - the JSON response returned from a registration request
        parseErrorListener - an error listener in the event the user ID cannot be parsed
        Returns:
        an integer representing the user ID

      • changeUserID

        public void changeUserID​(int uid)
        Alters the user ID for the app's SharedPreferences to keep track of the user's identity. If the ID is set to a value indicating that an error has occurred, this method automatically returns without doing anything.
        Parameters:
        uid - the user ID to attempt to put into SharedPreferences; if -404, nothing happens
